description:
This replication package contains the interview guide used for the paper&nbsp; &quot;We Feel Like We&#39;re Winging It:&quot; A Study on Navigating Open-Source Dependency Abandonment  (ESEC/FSE 2023) along with a table with summary statistics for the interviewees.&nbsp; 


	 intervieweeSummaryTable.pdf is&nbsp;a table with the summary statistics for the 33 interview participants. 
	 interviewGuide.pdf is the final iteration of the interview guide used for the semi-structured exploratory interviews. 


 For more details on the interview protocol and sampling method please see Sections 3.1 and 3.2 of the paper  pre-print here .&nbsp;

